  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this investigation is to carry out a clinical evaluation of a newly developed
      fistula pouching system's ability to function as a good pouch for fistulas, with the opening
      on the skin of the stomach or in a wound on the skin of the stomach.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
